			y: -3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["75C157B691AC5AFE"]
			description: ["The Pure Daisy is placed in the world and converts adjacent Stone into Livingrock and Wood into Livingwood over time — the foundational materials for all Botania infrastructure. Craft two and let them work passively while you tend to other progression. You will need substantial Livingrock quantities before long."]
