		}
		{
			dependencies: ["503C916FBA9B26FD"]
			description: ["Qi Crystal Ore generates at diamond depth and emits a faint luminescence. Mine it raw and smelt it to obtain Qi Crystals — a key reagent in Soul Land forging recipes and a catalyst used in Botania's mana infusion gate for Spirit Steel. Keep a stockpile; demand increases significantly as you advance."]
