		{
			dependencies: ["6CD3FDD027906C44"]
			description: ["The Runic Altar uses mana and materials to craft Runes — the building blocks of Botania's highest-tier recipes. Each rune represents one of the classical elements. To craft a rune, place the ingredients on the altar, then right-click with your Wand of the Forest while it holds sufficient mana."]
