		{
			dependencies: ["738DA05E474241BB"]
			description: ["The Water Rod conjures a temporary water source at the target location. A practical exploration and farming tool at modest mana cost. Useful for creating waterfalls, filling tanks, or placing water sources in the Nether where conventional water placement is blocked."]
