		{
			dependencies: ["46D9C86A05048965"]
			description: ["The Tornado Rod launches you into the air and grants a brief upward burst of momentum. Combined with Paragliders, this effectively gives you controlled aerial traversal without a full elytra setup. Keep it charged — it can save your life in difficult terrain."]
