			dependencies: ["1D2F06656F6C6EC8"]
			description: ["The Dirt Rod summons a column of dirt from below the target location, up to a fixed height. Useful for bridging gaps, scaling cliffs, or rapidly placing terrain without consuming inventory materials. A practical utility tool at very low mana cost."]
