		{
			dependencies: ["6DACE8982D9E9FA0"]
			description: ["Blood Magic draws power from Life Points — your own vitality. The Blood Altar is the heart of the system; sacrifice your health into it using the Sacrificial Dagger, or sacrifice mobs via a Well of Suffering ritual. As your altar tier rises, access to sigils, orbs, and rituals expands. Blood Magic power scales far beyond what early-game alternatives can match."]
